d 'MYSUITE': module providing built-in extensible program suite for empirical research
d
d     mysuite is a comprehensive Stata program suite designed for
d empirical research, teaching management,    and academic writing.
d It provides access to 30 specialized programs organized into
d three main	categories. 
d
d KW: program management
d KW: research tools
d
d Requires: Stata version 18 
d
